  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 39,
      "chapterTitle": "六 马克斯主义",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "925256_10_8179-8242",
          "range": "8110-8173",
          "rangeStart": 8110,
          "rangeEnd": 8173,
          "markText": "因此，马克斯主义分子的诉求自相矛盾，“拒绝我，那么我就爱你。不要准时打电话给我，那么我就吻你。不要和我上床，那么我就崇拜你。”",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1701442708,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-12-01 22:58:28",
          "chapterUid": 39,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=925256&chapterUid=39&rangeStart=8110&rangeEnd=8173",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b8321d05e1e481b865ba0e?chapterUid=39&rangeStart=8110&rangeEnd=8173"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "chapterTitle": "三 诱惑的潜台词",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "925256_7_430-600",
          "range": "1010-1180",
          "rangeStart": 1010,
          "rangeEnd": 1180,
          "markText": "对于坠入情网的人们而言，恋人的任何言行举止似乎都有了潜台词。每一点微笑的意蕴、每一个词语的含义都如一条小路，通向即使没有一万二千个，至少也有十二个。日常生活中（即没有爱情的生活）可以按其表面意义理解的姿势和话语，现在却要穷尽词典可能有的所有释义。至少对倾慕者而言，所有的疑虑都归结到一个中心问题，如同罪人惊惶地等待判决一般：她/他喜欢我吗？",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1701407538,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2023-12-01 13:12:18",
          "chapterUid": 36,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=925256&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=1010&rangeEnd=1180",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b8321d05e1e481b865ba0e?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=1010&rangeEnd=1180"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "925256_33_1985-2004",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "1985-2004",
      "markText": "我们先有爱的需要，然后再爱一个特定的人",
      "totalCount": 2574,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=925256&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=1985&rangeEnd=2004",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b8321d05e1e481b865ba0e?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=1985&rangeEnd=2004"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "925256_35_1246-1318",
      "chapterUid": 35,
      "range": "1246-1318",
      "markText": "每一例一见钟情中都有对爱人品质的故意夸张。这种夸张的赞美使我们只会把精力倾注在一张特定的脸上，这张脸承载着我们草率而神奇的信念，不致使理想破灭。",
      "totalCount": 2296,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=925256&chapterUid=35&rangeStart=1246&rangeEnd=1318",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b8321d05e1e481b865ba0e?chapterUid=35&rangeStart=1246&rangeEnd=1318"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "925256_35_5188-5230",
      "chapterUid": 35,
      "range": "5188-5230",
      "markText": "然而只有在不了解所爱之人时，我们才会跌入爱河，最初的行动必然建立在茫无所知的基础上。",
      "totalCount": 2288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=925256&chapterUid=35&rangeStart=5188&rangeEnd=5230",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b8321d05e1e481b865ba0e?chapterUid=35&rangeStart=5188&rangeEnd=5230"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "925256_32_2406-2479",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "2406-2479",
      "markText": "事实上，每个读者只能读到已然存在于他内心的东西。书籍只不过是一种光学仪器，作者将其提供给读者，以便于他发现如果没有这本书的帮助他就发现不了的东西。",
      "totalCount": 2268,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=925256&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=2406&rangeEnd=2479",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b8321d05e1e481b865ba0e?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=2406&rangeEnd=2479"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "925256_34_1008-1050",
      "chapterUid": 34,
      "range": "1008-1050",
      "markText": "恋爱时，我们最向往缘分天定。然而，多数时候我们不得不与无法理解我们灵魂的人同榻共枕。",
      "totalCount": 2016,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=925256&chapterUid=34&rangeStart=1008&rangeEnd=1050",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b8321d05e1e481b865ba0e?chapterUid=34&rangeStart=1008&rangeEnd=1050"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "925256_32_1932-1972",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "1932-1972",
      "markText": "最好的书能清楚地阐明你长久以来一直心有所感，却从来没办法明白表达出来的那些东西。",
      "totalCount": 1854,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=925256&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=1932&rangeEnd=1972",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b8321d05e1e481b865ba0e?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=1932&rangeEnd=1972"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "925256_34_3187-3210",
      "chapterUid": 34,
      "range": "3187-3210",
      "markText": "惟有生命走到尽头，我们才能知道自己的爱之所在。",
      "totalCount": 1830,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=925256&chapterUid=34&rangeStart=3187&rangeEnd=3210",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/1b8321d05e1e481b865ba0e?chapterUid=34&rangeStart=3187&rangeEnd=3210"
